  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/0cfebc344eb126e2f4bc4cc3874512758d4bfa0f" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:47.863ex; height:3.176ex;" alt="{\displaystyle (a_{1})+(a_{2}x+a_{2})+(a_{3}x^{2}+a_{3}x+a_{3})=x^{2}-1}"></span></dd></dl>
<p>and collecting like powers of <i>x</i>, we&#160;get
</p>
<dl><dd><span class="mwe-math-element"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"  alttext="{\displaystyle a_{3}x^{2}+(a_{2}+a_{3})x+(a_{1}+a_{2}+a_{3})=1x^{2}+0x+(-1).}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
